 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hcs1665702693913.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hcs1665702693913.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hcs1665702693913.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hcs1665702693913\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__uprmtype_408149\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the data type of the specified parameter or entity field.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__topic_d123467e1_d123468e1_d123469e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hcs1665702693913_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__codeblock_qxl_lbk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uprmtype (UHACThParam, int*pType);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__topic_d87262e1_d87263e1_d87264e1_d87265e1_d87266e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259257e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__parml_sjd_nbk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hParam</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle to the parameter or entity field</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">pType</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Parameter or field type (see below for possible values) (Output)</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__topic_d87267e1_d87268e1_d87269e1_d87270e1_d87271e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259257e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by uprmtype</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__2\">Success.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__1\">-165</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14978e1_d14979e1_d14980e1__entry__2\">The supplied handle is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__p_d123485e1_d123486e1_d123487e1\">The value returned in the variable <var class=\"keyword varname\">pType</var> can be any of the following:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned (variable pType)</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">Mnemonic</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_UNKNOWN</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_STRING</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_BOOLEAN</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_NUMERIC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_FLOAT</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">5</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_DATE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">6</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_TIME</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">7</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_DATETIME</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_LDATE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_LTIME</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">10</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_LDATETIME</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">11</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_RAW</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">12</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_IMAGE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">13</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_ENTITY</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">14</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_OCC</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">15</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_INCL_ENTITY</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__1\">16</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hcs1665702693913__table_d14981e1_d14982e1_d14983e1__entry__2\">UTYPE_HANDLE</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__p_d123488e1_d123489e1_d123490e1\">These mnemonics are defined in <span class=\"ph filepath\">h3gl.h</span>, and we recommend that you use them rather than the actual values.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__topic_d87272e1_d87273e1_d87274e1_d87275e1_d87276e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259257e337\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__topic_d87277e1_d87278e1_d87279e1_d87280e1_d87281e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259257e349\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__p_d123500e1_d123501e1_d123502e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uprmtype</code> returns the data type of\n            the specified operation parameter or entity field. To call this function, you must first\n            obtain a handle to the parameter or entity field by calling <code class=\"ph codeph\">uprmgeth</code>\n            (unlike <code class=\"ph codeph\">uprmdir</code>, which does not require a parameter handle).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__section_wlb_1ck_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259257e366\">Example: uoprprms, uniname, uprmdir, and uprmtype</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following routine prints out a list of the parameters of an arbitrary\n            operation in an arbitrary component.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hcs1665702693913_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__codeblock_qyy_cck_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nchar *types[] = { \"Unknown\", \"String\", \"Boolean\", \"Numeric\", \"Float\", \"Date\", \"Time\",\n\"DateTime\",\"LinearDate\", \"LinearTime\", \"LinearDateTime\", \"Raw\", \"Image\", \"Entity\",\n\"Occurrence\", \"IncludedEntity\", \"Handle\" };\nchar *dires[] = { \"Unknown\", \"In\", \"Out\", \"InOut\" };\n\nvoid inspect_operation_params (char *svcname, char *oprname)\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn, hOp, hParm;\nlong i, nParams;\nint pType, pDir;\nchar name[1+UPRMNAMESIZE];\nchar* template1 = \" %3s %-20s %-20s %s\\n\";\nchar* template2 = \" %3d %-20s %-20s %s\\n\";\n\nueopen(&amp;hEnv);\nuinstnew(hEnv, (UCHAR*)svcname, 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, 0);\nuinstopr(hIn, (UCHAR*)oprname, 0, &amp;hOp);\nprintf(\"Parameters of operation %s in service %s:\\n\\n\", oprname, svcname);\nprintf(template1, \"Num\", \"Name \", \"Type \",\n\"Direction\");\nprintf(template1, \"===\", \"====================\", \"====================\",\n\"=========\");\n\nuoprprms(hOp, &amp;nParams);\nfor ( i=1; i&lt;=nParams; i++ )\n{\nuprmdir(hOp, i, &amp;pDir);\nuprmgeth(hOp, i, 0, &amp;hParm);\nuprmtype(hParm, &amp;pType);\nuniname(hOp, i, UPRMNAMESIZE, name);\n\nprintf(template2, i, name, types[pType], dires[pDir]);\n}\nprintf(\"\\n\");\n\nuinstdel(hIn, 0);\nufreeh(&amp;hOp);\nufreeh(&amp;hIn);\nufreeh(&amp;hEnv);\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Here is an example of output generated by this function:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hcs1665702693913_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hcs1665702693913__codeblock_y1h_fck_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Parameters of operation MYOP in service TESTSVC:\n\nNum Name Type Direction\n=== ==================== ==================== =========\n1 P1 Numeric In\n2 P2 String InOut\n3 P3 Date Out</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oud1665702693770.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uoprprms</a><p>Return the number of parameters in the specified operation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ajt1665702693842.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uprmdir</a><p>Return the direction (in/out/inout) of the specified parameter.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pdl1665702693580.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uprmgeth</a><p>Get the handle of the specified operation parameter or entity field. Or detach a parameter from an operation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528150\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528150\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uprmtype Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the data type of the specified parameter or entity field. Explain this code long uprmtype (UHACThParam, int*pType); Copy Parameters hParam Handle to the parameter or entity field pType Parameter or field type (see below for possible values) (Output) Return Values Table 1. Values returned by uprmtype Value Meaning 0 Success. -165 The supplied handle is not valid. The value returned in the variable pType can be any of the following: Table 2. Values returned (variable pType) Value Mnemonic 0 UTYPE_UNKNOWN 1 UTYPE_STRING 2 UTYPE_BOOLEAN 3 UTYPE_NUMERIC 4 UTYPE_FLOAT 5 UTYPE_DATE 6 UTYPE_TIME 7 UTYPE_DATETIME 8 UTYPE_LDATE 9 UTYPE_LTIME 10 UTYPE_LDATETIME 11 UTYPE_RAW 12 UTYPE_IMAGE 13 UTYPE_ENTITY 14 UTYPE_OCC 15 UTYPE_INCL_ENTITY 16 UTYPE_HANDLE These mnemonics are defined in h3gl.h , and we recommend that you use them rather than the actual values. Use Library: ucall Description uprmtype returns the data type of the specified operation parameter or entity field. To call this function, you must first obtain a handle to the parameter or entity field by calling uprmgeth (unlike uprmdir , which does not require a parameter handle). Example: uoprprms, uniname, uprmdir, and uprmtype The following routine prints out a list of the parameters of an arbitrary operation in an arbitrary component. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> char *types[] = { \"Unknown\", \"String\", \"Boolean\", \"Numeric\", \"Float\", \"Date\", \"Time\", \"DateTime\",\"LinearDate\", \"LinearTime\", \"LinearDateTime\", \"Raw\", \"Image\", \"Entity\", \"Occurrence\", \"IncludedEntity\", \"Handle\" }; char *dires[] = { \"Unknown\", \"In\", \"Out\", \"InOut\" }; void inspect_operation_params (char *svcname, char *oprname) { UHACT hEnv, hIn, hOp, hParm; long i, nParams; int pType, pDir; char name[1+UPRMNAMESIZE]; char* template1 = \" %3s %-20s %-20s %s\\n\"; char* template2 = \" %3d %-20s %-20s %s\\n\"; ueopen(&hEnv); uinstnew(hEnv, (UCHAR*)svcname, 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, 0); uinstopr(hIn, (UCHAR*)oprname, 0, &hOp); printf(\"Parameters of operation %s in service %s:\\n\\n\", oprname, svcname); printf(template1, \"Num\", \"Name \", \"Type \", \"Direction\"); printf(template1, \"===\", \"====================\", \"====================\", \"=========\"); uoprprms(hOp, &nParams); for ( i=1; i<=nParams; i++ ) { uprmdir(hOp, i, &pDir); uprmgeth(hOp, i, 0, &hParm); uprmtype(hParm, &pType); uniname(hOp, i, UPRMNAMESIZE, name); printf(template2, i, name, types[pType], dires[pDir]); } printf(\"\\n\"); uinstdel(hIn, 0); ufreeh(&hOp); ufreeh(&hIn); ufreeh(&hEnv); } Copy Here is an example of output generated by this function: Explain this code Parameters of operation MYOP in service TESTSVC: Num Name Type Direction === ==================== ==================== ========= 1 P1 Numeric In 2 P2 String InOut 3 P3 Date Out Copy Related Links uoprprms Return the number of parameters in the specified operation. uprmdir Return the direction (in/out/inout) of the specified parameter. uprmgeth Get the handle of the specified operation parameter or entity field. Or detach a parameter from an operation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}